Class ActorLevelUp

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.Node
javafx.scene.Parent
javafx.scene.Group
com.example.demo.actors.Actor.Actor
com.example.demo.actors.Actor.ActorLevelUp
All Implemented Interfaces:
Destructible, javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
public class ActorLevelUp extends Actor
The ActorLevelUp class represents a power-up actor that grants the player increased firepower upon collection. It moves in a sinusoidal pattern across the screen and is destroyed when collected or when it moves off the screen.
